<div class='col-lg-7 col-lg-offset-1'>
<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='498' id='t-498'>So I'd like you to come back with me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='3157' id='t-3157'>just for a few minutes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5058' id='t-5058'>to a dark night in China,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='7927' id='t-7927'>the night I met my husband.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10648' id='t-10648'>It was a city so long ago that it was still called</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='14091' id='t-14091'>Peking.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16204' id='t-16204'>So I went to a party.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18825' id='t-18825'>I sat down next to a stout, middle-aged man</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='22208' id='t-22208'>with owl glasses and a bow tie,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='25722' id='t-25722'>and he turned out to be a Fulbright scholar,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='28615' id='t-28615'>there in China specifically to study</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='32179' id='t-32179'>Sino-Soviet relations.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='34270' id='t-34270'>What a gift it was to the eager,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='36670' id='t-36670'>young foreign correspondent that I was then.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='39428' id='t-39428'>I'd pump him for information,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='41436' id='t-41436'>I'm mentally scribbling notes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='43093' id='t-43093'>for the stories I plan to write.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='45402' id='t-45402'>I talk to him for hours.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47887' id='t-47887'>Only months later,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='51398' id='t-51398'>I discover who he really was.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='53772' id='t-53772'>He was the China representative</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='56545' id='t-56545'>for the American Soybean Association.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='60774' id='t-60774'>&quot;I don't understand. Soybeans?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='64044' id='t-64044'>You told me you were a Fulbright scholar.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66799' id='t-66799'>&quot;Well, how long would you have talked to me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='68687' id='t-68687'>if I told you we're in soybeans?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='70729' id='t-70729'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='73210' id='t-73210'>I said, &quot;You jerk.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='76502' id='t-76502'>Only jerk wasn't the word I used.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='80255' id='t-80255'>I said, &quot;You could've gotten me fired.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='84402' id='t-84402'>And he said, &quot;Let's get married.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='87939' id='t-87939'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='89226' id='t-89226'>&quot;Travel the world and have lots of kids.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='92122' id='t-92122'>So we did.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94220' id='t-94220'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96265' id='t-96265'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='101507' id='t-101507'>And what an alive man Terence Bryan Foley</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='105247' id='t-105247'>turned out to be.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='106694' id='t-106694'>He was a Chinese scholar</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='108337' id='t-108337'>who later, in his 60s,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110203' id='t-110203'>got a Ph.D. in Chinese history.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='112755' id='t-112755'>He spoke six languages,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='115243' id='t-115243'>he played 15 musical instruments,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='117731' id='t-117731'>he was a licensed pilot,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='119507' id='t-119507'>he had once been a San Francisco cable car operator,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122678' id='t-122678'>he was an expert in swine nutrition,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='125512' id='t-125512'>dairy cattle, Dixieland jazz, film noir,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='129293' id='t-129293'>and we did travel the country, and the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='133477' id='t-133477'>and we did have a lot of kids.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='135706' id='t-135706'>We followed my job, and it seemed like</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137448' id='t-137448'>there was nothing that we couldn't do.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141015' id='t-141015'>So when we found the cancer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144797' id='t-144797'>it doesn't seem strange to us at all</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='147362' id='t-147362'>that without saying a word to each other,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='149995' id='t-149995'>we believed that,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152421' id='t-152421'>if we were smart enough</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154680' id='t-154680'>and strong enough and brave enough,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='159011' id='t-159011'>and we worked hard enough,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='161484' id='t-161484'>we could keep him from dying ever.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='166762' id='t-166762'>And for years, it seemed like we were succeeding.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='170261' id='t-170261'>The surgeon emerged from the surgery.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173140' id='t-173140'>What'd he say? He said what surgeons always say:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='175417' id='t-175417'>&quot;We got it all.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='177419' id='t-177419'>Then there was a setback when the pathologists</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='180462' id='t-180462'>looked at the kidney cancer closely.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='182835' id='t-182835'>It turned out to be a rare,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='184464' id='t-184464'>exceedingly aggressive type,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='186273' id='t-186273'>with a diagnosis that was almost universally fatal</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='189355' id='t-189355'>in several weeks at most.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='191746' id='t-191746'>And yet, he did not die.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195456' id='t-195456'>Mysteriously, he lived on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='198966' id='t-198966'>He coached Little League for our son.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201050' id='t-201050'>He built a playhouse for our daughter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203602' id='t-203602'>And meanwhile, I'm burying myself in the Internet</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='206676' id='t-206676'>looking for specialists.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='208350' id='t-208350'>I'm looking for a cure.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='210911' id='t-210911'>So a year goes by</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='212988' id='t-212988'>before the cancer, as cancers do,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='216194' id='t-216194'>reappears,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='218194' id='t-218194'>and with it comes another death sentence,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='220270' id='t-220270'>this time nine months.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='222463' id='t-222463'>So we try another treatment, aggressive, nasty.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226477' id='t-226477'>It makes him so sick, he has to quit it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228297' id='t-228297'>yet still he lives on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231314' id='t-231314'>Then another year goes by.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='233210' id='t-233210'>Two years go by.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='234760' id='t-234760'>More specialists.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='236249' id='t-236249'>We take the kids to Italy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='238169' id='t-238169'>We take the kids to Australia.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='240638' id='t-240638'>And then more years pass,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243350' id='t-243350'>and the cancer begins to grow.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='245740' id='t-245740'>This time, there's new treatments on the horizon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='248275' id='t-248275'>They're exotic. They're experimental.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='250211' id='t-250211'>They're going to attack the cancer in new ways.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='253419' id='t-253419'>So he enters a clinical trial, and it works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='257745' id='t-257745'>The cancer begins to shrink,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='259674' id='t-259674'>and for the third time,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='261951' id='t-261951'>we've dodged death.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='265310' id='t-265310'>So now I ask you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='268607' id='t-268607'>how do I feel</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='270996' id='t-270996'>when the time finally comes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='273510' id='t-273510'>and there's another dark night,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='276016' id='t-276016'>sometime between midnight and 2 a.m.?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278517' id='t-278517'>This time it's on the intensive care ward</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='281491' id='t-281491'>when a twentysomething resident</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283329' id='t-283329'>that I've never met before</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='285532' id='t-285532'>tells me that Terence is dying,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288125' id='t-288125'>perhaps tonight.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='290324' id='t-290324'>So what do I say when he says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293117' id='t-293117'>&quot;What do you want me to do?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:06
</data>
